author: Jennifer Hansler, CNN
title: State Department says it has repatriated 9,000 Americans amid coronavirus pandemic
description: The State Department has repatriated more than 9,000 Americans from 28 countries amid the coronavirus pandemic, State Department spokesperson Morgan Ortagus said Tuesday.
content:
Washington (CNN)The State Department has repatriated more than 9,000 Americans from 28 countries amid the coronavirus pandemic, State Department spokesperson Morgan Ortagus said Tuesday.
